Re: 疑問文の語尾につく「わけ?」はどういう意味ですか?
by NileCat » Sat 12.18.2010 9:41 am Thank you, Hyperworm! EDIT:If I used the words "your story" to explain the meaning of "わけ", does it make sense in English?～ is your story?I mean, I've noticed わけ is not always used to mean the reason.e.g. ま、こういったわけでして could be translated like "that's the story", I think. NileCat
